{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述孔雀这一可怕角色的登场。孔雀手持天下无双的暗器孔雀翎，外表平凡内心扭曲。明月心向傅红雪揭示孔雀的秘密：孔雀翎已不在孔雀山庄，而是落入孔雀手中。杜雷约战傅红雪于倪家废园，明月心建议将燕南飞送往孔雀山庄避难。傅红雪发现明月心暗中倒掉燕南飞的解药，揭示她与燕南飞之间的阴谋。本章引入孔雀这一强大反派，展现傅红雪与明月心之间的心理博弈。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才那个人，你当然也看见过吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你并没有注意到他，因为他实在太平凡……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我一直认为这种人最可怕。若不是他刚才自己露出了行迹，也许你直到现在还不会注意他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他要查探我们的行迹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我们还没有看出他的来历，他已看见了我们，不出一个时辰，他就会查出燕南飞在什么地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黑手也和燕南飞有仇？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有，他们从不会因为自己的仇恨而杀人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们只为什么杀人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "命令。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们也听人的命令？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只听一个人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子羽！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就凭黑手他们五个人，还没有成立这种组织的力量。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "普天之下，只有一个人有这种力量。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子羽？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有他！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以杀止杀，你刚才本该杀了那个人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你从不轻易拔刀，可是他已值得你拔刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认为他就是无名指？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我甚至怀疑他就是孔雀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孔雀？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孔雀是种鸟，很美丽的鸟，尤其是它的翎……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你说的孔雀却不是鸟？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说的不是鸟，是人，是个很可怕的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我甚至认为他就是天下最可怕的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他有孔雀翎！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当然也知道孔雀翎！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你却决不会知道，孔雀翎已不在'孔雀山庄'里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是个秘密。江湖中从来也没有人知道这个秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这秘密直到现在才渐渐有人知道，因为孔雀翎忽然又在江湖中出现了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要孔雀翎存在一天，江湖中就没有人敢来侵犯孔雀山庄，否则这地方就会被毁灭。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孔雀山庄三百年的声名，八十里的基业，五百条人命，其实都建筑在一个小小的孔雀翎上！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个人就是孔雀？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就知道你一定有法子引他们出来的，你做的事从来没有失败过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看见了他们？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女的是明月心，男的是傅红雪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕南飞还能活到现在，就因为傅红雪，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以要杀燕南飞，必须先杀傅红雪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你很想杀傅红雪？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一向喜欢杀人，傅红雪也是人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他却不是个普通人，要杀他并不是件容易事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道，所以我并不想自己动手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不动，还有谁敢动？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不动，只因为我不是名人，也不想出名。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想叫杜雷先去拼命，你好在后面捡便宜？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论他们是谁死在谁手里，至少我都不会难受的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕公子醒过没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你喂他吃过药？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也没有。没有姑娘的吩咐，我连碰都不敢碰他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我怕姑娘吃醋！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在是不是已到了应该吃药的时候？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吃过了这次药，再好好地睡一觉，我想他明天早上就应该醒过来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道杜雷一定会找上你的，却想不到他来得这么快！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倪家废园在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在对面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是个跛子，我不喜欢在决战前走得太远！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你准备去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人，一把刀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好，好极了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天晚上，你可以好好睡一觉。明天吃过早饭，只要走几步路，就到倪家废园了，一定还有足够的时间，先去看看那里的地形。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杜雷是个什么样的人，你也已观察得很清楚，他却完全不了解你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以这一战你实在已占尽了先机，到时候只要你一拔你的刀，江湖名人榜上，就只剩下十二个人了。就算你并不十分喜欢杀人，这也应该算是件很愉快的事！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是燕南飞呢？你有没有想到他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要去决斗的人，并不是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要死的人却一定是他！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孔雀和拇指现在一定已知道他的下落，只要你走进倪家废园，他们就会闯进这屋子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许你以前救过他的命，可是这一次若是没有你，他也许反而会活得长久些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的关心他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道我不该去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然应该去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是在你还没有去之前，就应该先把他送到一个安全的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么地方安全？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孔雀山庄！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说过，孔雀翎已不在孔雀山庄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，孔雀山庄现在还有什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有秋水清。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他虽然一向很保守，可是你送去的人，他是决不会拒绝的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他欠你的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欠我什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "欠你一条命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你虽然一向很少救人，却救过他，而且救过他两次，一次在渭水之滨，一次在泰山之阴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在他已是孔雀山庄的庄主，他已有足够的力量还债。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是他已没有孔雀翎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家一直都认为，孔雀山庄的基业，完全是建筑在孔雀翎上的，直到现在，大家才知道秋水清这个人远比孔雀翎更可怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孔雀翎已落入外姓手里，这消息在江湖中流传得很快，孔雀山庄的仇家却很多，这两年来，至少已有六批人去袭击过孔雀山庄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这六批人，一共有七十九个，每个人都是一流高手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "结果呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这七十九位高手，一入孔雀山庄，就好像石沉大海，连一点消息都没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最后一批人，是在去年重阳时去的，自从那一次之后，江湖中就没有人敢再妄入孔雀山庄一步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孔雀山庄距离这里并不远，我们轻车快马赶去，明天正午之前，一定可以赶回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不怕他们在路上拦截？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖中有谁能拦得住你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至少有一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "带着孔雀翎的孔雀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他决不敢出手的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孔雀翎虽然是天下无双的暗器，他这人却不是天下无双的高手，他怕你的刀比他的出手快！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若真的不愿让他死在别人手里，现在就应该带我们去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可以带你们去，但却有句话要问你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你问吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若真的关心他，为什么要把他的解药倒在别人衣袖里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说过，我早就说过，要骗他并不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也知道不容易，可是我一定要试一试。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你已试过了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我试过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你觉得怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ming_yue_xin",
      "speaker_name": "明月心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只觉得要骗他实在很不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我却还要试一试！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5
    }
  ],
